dct_description_sm: Map shows statistical and local government area boundaries, roads. Fremantle and sububs boundaries are shown with hatched lines. Boundaries are as used in Census 30 June 1954. This map is supplementary to state map : Statistical divisions of Western Australia / National Mapping Office. [Canberra] : The Bureau, [1954]. Map Collection does not have this map.
